    <h2>About AgHire</h2>
    <p>AgHire is an app for Farmers, Staff, and Contractors to connect and find agricultural equipment and skilled operators in Australia.</p>

    <h2>Getting Help</h2>
    <p>If you have questions, issues, or feedback, please reach out via email: <a href="mailto:aghire.au@gmail.com">aghire.au@gmail.com</a></p>

    <h2>FAQ</h2>
    <p><strong>Q: How do I create a listing?</strong><br>
       A: Tap "Create New Listing" in the app, fill in the required fields, add images, and submit.</p>

    <p><strong>Q: Can I use AgHire outside Australia?</strong><br>
       A: Currently, AgHire is only available for listings and users in Australia.</p>

    <p><strong>Q: How can I advertise?</strong><br>
       A: AgHire is currently accepting advertisers. Contact us for more information on promoting your equipment or services through the app.</p>

